column5: I am still waiting on Jef.... I gave him a beauty lure.... still waiting tap tap tap..  LOL!  Gerritt.
Ummm........Glen................tjsa here, wink, wink, nudge, nudge,
Those are just too pretty to use
WTG Glen...those are some of the best spinnerbaits I've ever used. I think Jef'll have a booth at the Muskie Odyssey. Should be interesting to see how long it takes for him to be sold out.
Can I borrow one of those ?
hey greencoachdog,let me get them broke in for you...  lol...lol...lol
Nice baits Glen  What you going to do with them?  Send em up I'll test them for ya!  Whopper
Do you even know how to fish for musky G?  Want some help wink, wink, nudge, nudge.   Sweet baits.  Joey
He probably has just as much of a clue what to do with them as does Wayne
If I'm nice can I borrow the third one??
A little overkill for 'Bamma Crappies, eh Glen?  Nice baits. I remember bidding up to $160 for those....
Nice! Now move farther north and you can use them more often! LOL
Who knew that Joey was a Muskie in disguise ? I think she is after Glens new lures......  Art
Those are fantastic looking spinnerbaits, I'll bet they do a lot of catching for you, Glen...  Mike
Greencoachdog,  Great looking baits - nicely done, Jeff.
